    "This ensures that the models make predictions that are fair and accurate for all people, regardless of their background (Nemani et al., 2023).",
    "(b) Debiasing frameworks: using systems based on principles of fairness and incorporating mechanisms to eliminate bias during training can help increase the objectivity of the results (Zhao et al., 2017).",
    "For instance, models with adversarial approaches that target specific biases can be used (Nemani et al., 2023).",
